Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.56,0:00:04.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What's new?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.02,0:00:06.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}This Kimono Jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.77,0:00:10.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh? That's a nice painting on the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.82,0:00:15.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's by a brilliant painter from a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.41,0:00:19.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Every now and then there's someone\Ncooking in these mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.50,0:00:26.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sometimes you see white things rising in the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.54,0:00:34.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Waving like the smoke from houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.59,0:00:45.48,ep-title-bg,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2100,3170)\p1\blur1}m 0 0 l 950 0 950 100 0 100
Dialogue: 1,0:00:36.59,0:00:45.48,ep-title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1500,1100)\be1}Clothes That Embrace the Mountain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.85,0:00:51.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I never knew someone's living so deep in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.40,0:00:56.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}No one lives any further than here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.16,0:01:00.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}But there's a lot of smoke rising.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:04.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Someone must be burning coal then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.21,0:01:08.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The mountain god is making dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:11.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gods cook too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.75,0:01:13.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}How else would they eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:16.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gods don't get hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:25.94,title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(816.19,585.905)\fad(3000,3000)\p1\blur1\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\3a&H00&\bord10\clip(675,530,957,642)\shad0}m 0 0 l 300 0 300 100 0 100
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:25.94,title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(814.857,585.906)\fad(3000,3000)}Mushishi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.55,0:01:19.35,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}He's taking a bath then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:21.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:26.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}hurry home and make our dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.52,0:01:27.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.85,0:01:28.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.41,0:01:50.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was something strange\Nin the mountains back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.38,0:01:55.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The mountain is still there just as it was,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:01:58.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but it's not the same as it was then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.34,0:02:06.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Back then, it was as if the village\Nwas embraced in a soft robe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.64,0:02:10.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sis, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.85,0:02:14.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I made it so that you wouldn't be a\Ndisgrace in front of your master.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.03,0:02:18.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knit it with the silk from silkworms in the mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:21.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and dyed it with the trees and grass from the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:26.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kai, if you can't come back, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:33.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad will forgive you if you become great.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:40.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But let this remind you of the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:45.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.56,0:02:50.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be sure to become a great artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:16.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to start painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:20.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what Sister and the others are up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:30.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:34.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wash those plates there please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:35.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:13.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's getting warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:19.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, come help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:20.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:33.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this your haori?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:37.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whose haura is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:40.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:44.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I just wanted to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.84,0:04:47.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:47.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:49.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:52.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't like it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:56.35,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:04:59.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come up to the painting room tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:04.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though there isn't much for me to teach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.29,0:05:20.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shoot, I'm out of paint.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:23.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just when I was almost done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:25.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:28.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,how's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:30.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The due date's close.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:33.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:37.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, what am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:41.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't have anyone I can borrow money from.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:43.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nothing to sell either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:49.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pretty raggy, isn't it? I can't give you much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:50.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:52.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll come back to get it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:06:00.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's an excellent piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:03.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure does have your touch to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:07.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's hard to believe you're still unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:10.09,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:11.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,How's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:15.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you make another one by next month?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.23,0:06:18.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My grandson has a wedding coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:22.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd be a great opportunity for\Nyou to become better known.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:26.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gladly! I'd love to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:42.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:45.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't be sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:54.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was very well received.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:57.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got all these requests.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:02.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm proud of you. I'm expecting great things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:05.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:10.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, how should I compose the next one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:17.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master, the mail for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:20.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, leave it there please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:31.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}More deadline reminders.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:33.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't they ever get tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:36.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Might as well save themselves the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:45.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:48.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a huge landslide.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:50.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard a whole village got swamped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:52.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could have been hit too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:57.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was some village at the skirts\Nof some mountain to the west.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:00.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:04.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can't be my village.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:07.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't be wasting my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:10.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is a precious time for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:14.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to get more famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:21.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's impressive. It sure is your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:25.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Sensei,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:28.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,are you sick or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:36.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The last piece I saw was literally flowing with life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:40.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I must be thinking too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:52.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:55.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:59.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You seem tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.64,0:09:02.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take some medicine and rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:04.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.23,0:09:06.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.60,0:09:11.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your fame is virtually set in stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:17.61,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kai,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:19.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}how do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:24.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Drink this, you'll feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:27.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,0:09:33.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How many years ago was it that she married?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:36.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder how she's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:39.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.22,0:09:42.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Would he forgive me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:47.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's been ten years since then, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:51.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I only remember them at times like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:53.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm so selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:56.78,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I want to see them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:10:01.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to walk through the scent of the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:07.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What am I so worried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:10.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.83,0:10:15.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure I'll be able to make good paintings again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:30.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:31.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:39.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Auntie?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:44.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Kai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:47.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:51.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your sister sent you a letter, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:56.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You haven't read it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:11:00.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must have been three years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:02.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a horrible landslide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:06.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most of the houses and farms got washed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:12.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We talked it over and decided to send you a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:19.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,To ask you to come back to help us with your fame.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:22.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about Dad and Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.95,0:11:26.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your dad died in the landslide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.75,0:11:34.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The next year, your sister gave birth to this kid and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:38.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't mean this in a bad way. Just go back to town.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:42.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't ever come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:57.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was a really popular painter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:12:00.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,One day he just vanished, and that was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:05.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That painting is worth quite a bit in itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:07.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:09.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:12.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's rather heavy for light silk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:15.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I do sense Mushi in it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:20.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could sell it to that collector doctor then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.88,0:12:22.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,How's this price?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:29.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You do say it hasn't caused any harm so far,\Nbut until we find out what it is, it's not safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:31.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't expect to sell it for much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:33.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll buy it for half of that price.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:36.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:39.78,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet you bought it for the price of a rag.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:44.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no, I'm sure you could figure\Nout what it is and sell it for a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:46.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd be bad if it were a pest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:52.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There aren't any Mushi-shi that would\Npay big bucks for stuff like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:53.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:54.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:12:56.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have one more piece of information.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:13:00.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's said that this mountain is\Nat the painter's home village.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:03.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,How's that, doesn't that give you a good lead?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:05.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Half price.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.85,0:13:09.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:22.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:25.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But please, you must return.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:29.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:36.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't paint anything anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:43.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing comes to mind when I pick up my brush.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:51.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The mountain looks like a stranger to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:57.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like I'm a stranger to the villagers here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:03.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I might as well move off to nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:11.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:19.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can taste the mountain's soil.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:43.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't get dizzy these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:46.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel light too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:52.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Toyo, are you alone again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:54.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm taking these to your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:56.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is Auntie home?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:14:59.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Auntie went cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.63,0:15:05.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are we going to do about the kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:07.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He has relatives on his father's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:11.09,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're far, but we'll have to give him to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.22,0:15:13.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:15.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me take care of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:17.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.85,0:15:22.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's slow growing and slow learning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:24.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You couldn't take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:29.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll take good care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:30.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:33.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please don't send him off afar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:40.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Toyo, hold this please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:44.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:49.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not right. Give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:52.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That'll just tip right over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.22,0:15:56.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, don't spill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:02.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's already five years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:05.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But he's still a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.32,0:16:07.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:23.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:25.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give it to your nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:28.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's gonna love this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:41.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.69,0:16:45.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The mountain's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.07,0:16:51.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's that smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:16:59.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:10.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:12.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought I was going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:15.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew I shouldn't have bought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.47,0:17:19.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:22.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm not anyone suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.94,0:17:27.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's light.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:29.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:32.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's my haori.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:41.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I searched for this mountain in the painting\Nto figure out what type of Mushi it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:47.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But as soon as I got into the mountain,\Nsomething strange happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:53.51,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:17:56.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My luggage is getting heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:17:59.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:07.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I finally got out of the dirt,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.65,0:18:09.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,the Mushi were gone from the haori.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:14.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:18.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Mushi in the haori seem to\Nhave been this land's Ubusuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:21.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ubusuna?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.58,0:18:25.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're a dirt-like Mushi that have\Ntheir own specific habitats.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:29.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though they're only in dirt form\Nwhen they're underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:32.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They seem to become a smoggy mist when they rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:35.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There seems to have been a huge landslide here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:40.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,A lot of the Ubusuna must have gotten\Nwashed away when that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:47.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those Ubusuna found this haori,\Nand attached themselves to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:50.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There seemed to be a lot of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:55.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ubusuna can't live in other lands,\Nso they must have gathered in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.94,0:18:59.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This cloth was made here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.11,0:19:01.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:06.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My sister made it for me entirely out of\Nmaterials from here in the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.41,0:19:13.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could recall the smells and sounds of the mountain\Nwith it when I first left the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:16.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ubusuna gather where there's the scent of their home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:21.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They exist in small amounts in all plants that grow there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:27.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And humans take in Ubusuna when they eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:30.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because they're so abundant they're not very strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:34.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and they lose all influence once the host leaves his land.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:38.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It does seem to try to protect you from other Mushi
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.11,0:19:42.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,once you return to your home town though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:47.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it have anything to do with a kid's slow growth?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:53.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It might happen if he doesn't get enough\NUbusuna during his weaning period.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.38,0:19:59.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,In which case, a lot of Ubusuna returned to this land,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.88,0:20:05.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,so he should catch up in time if\Nyou give him lots of local food.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.77,0:20:08.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:13.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you don't need this haori anymore, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.94,0:20:16.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you sell it to me, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:20.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was planning on selling it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.24,0:20:21.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:24.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's precious to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:29.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:31.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But on one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:36.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,A haori with Ubusuna in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:39.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:39.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.67,0:20:44.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Smoke rises from the mountain\Nin the painting once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.43,0:20:48.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,In a while? How often?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.18,0:20:51.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once in ten years, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.56,0:20:53.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That really is once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.31,0:20:59.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The painting sure is nice too though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.36,0:21:00.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:03.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's by a mysterious ingenious artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:06.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanna see it come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.53,0:21:08.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, it almost got me killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.54,0:21:11.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure I'm not guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:15.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,On this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.79,0:21:17.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. The same painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.96,0:21:22.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you not have paint?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.01,0:21:26.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:47.78,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:49.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.12,0:21:51.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, Toyo, it's the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:53.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Draw more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:56.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.96,0:21:57.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,here goes.
